room_title: Escape room "Doomsday" by Bust Out Escape Room in Albuquerque
room_address: 9440 San Mateo Blvd Suite K Albuquerque, NM 87113
room_description: Your team of soldiers is tasked with saving the nation from WWIII. Your team will start the adventure in an abandoned bunker that holds a retired nuclear device that may destroy the threats. You only have one hour to make your way through the room before certain destruction. Therefore, your team should be fast and stealthy on this mission to escape in time.
